Source: linux-meta-grml
Section: kernel
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Grml Team <team@grml.org>
Standards-Version: 3.9.4
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8)
Vcs-Git: git://git.grml.org/grml-kernel.git
