Package: linux-image-amd64-grml
Architecture: amd64
Section: kernel
Depends: linux-image-3.7-6-grml-amd64
Description: The newest Linux kernel for amd64, Grml Edition
 This package is a meta-package that will always depend on the newest
 default Linux kernel image (Grml Edition) for amd64 (the arch).

